 treat for lovers of romance, crime, or mathematics.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Jul 2021) 0aCriminal investigationvFiction. 0aMathematicsvFiction. 0aMathematicsvMiscellanea. 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / General.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertPrinceton University Press Complete eBook-Package 2016z978311063859240uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9781400873388zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de Gruyter40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781400873388423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9781400873388.jpg  a978-3-11-063859-2  Princeton University Press Complete eBook-Package 2016b2016  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_LT  aEBA_EBACKALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_LT  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA5EBK